      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple though. \"rebuilding\" sounds like a joke when you're staring at a hole you can never fill. i feel like i've already died inside. like the person i was—the one they all believed in—is just gone. there is no \"rebuilding\" from this kind of disgrace. every time i close my eyes i just see their faces when they realize i ruined everything. it feels like the only way to actually stop the feeling is to just... make it stop. permanently.",
